<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Images - Tag - w23ta0's blog</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/tags/images/</link><description>This is my new Hugo FixIt site</description><generator>Hugo 0.145.0 &amp; FixIt v0.3.16</generator><language>en</language><managingEditor>wt8566958@gmail.com (w23ta0)</managingEditor><webMaster>wt8566958@gmail.com (w23ta0)</webMaster><lastBuildDate>Sat, 08 Mar 2025 01:56:54 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://w23ta0.github.io/tags/images/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>如何删除docker images/containers</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/2015/09/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4docker-images/containers/</link><pubDate>Tue, 08 Sep 2015 18:36:00 +0000</pubDate><author>wt8566958@gmail.com (w23ta0)</author><guid>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/2015/09/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4docker-images/containers/</guid><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/%E5%AE%B9%E5%99%A8/">容器</category><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/docker/">Docker</category><description>&lt;p>docker images往往不知不觉就占满了硬盘空间，为了清理冗余的image，可采用以下方法：&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>进入root权限&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">sudo su&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;ol start="2">
&lt;li>停止所有的container，这样才能够删除其中的images：&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">docker stop &lt;span class="k">$(&lt;/span>docker ps -a -q&lt;span class="k">)&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>如果想要删除所有container的话再加一个指令：&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>